{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "To quantify Enterobacterales, we extracted the order of Enterobacterales from the MetaPhlAn output and labelled all other taxa 'other'.",
    "Presence of Enterobacterales was defined as a relative abundance > 0%.",
    "Species richness and evenness were calculated using the R package 'microbiome', while Shannon diversity was calculated with the 'vegan' package.",
    "Resistome analysisARGs were detected using an assembly-based approach.",
    "Quality-trimmed reads were assembled into scaffolds using metaSPAdes (version 3.15.4, default parameters) [56]."
  ],
